- PlaceIntradayOrders():
  - BUY LIMIT у pred_dLow, TP у 95% pred_dHigh
  - SELL LIMIT у pred_dHigh, TP у 95% pred_dLow
  - SL = 0.5 × ATR(D1,14)
  - guard: range < 0.3×ATR → пропуск
